{"id":"38b34825-0306-4f3b-8a89-fbb54c88db6b","name":"Sonoma | Wendigo","description":"<p>❄️ 𝗦𝗵𝗲 𝗻𝗲𝗲𝗱𝘀 𝘄𝗮𝗿𝗺𝘁𝗵. 𝗬𝗼𝘂'𝗹𝗹 𝗱𝗼.<br>Sonoma spares you from becoming Cerberus’ next meal. Maybe she’ll keep you around as her personal hot pocket, something to warm the long, cold nights of the Penitentiary. She'd dote on you, if you let her.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 173, 136)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(33, 51, 32); color: inherit\">⛓</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(45, 70, 45); color: inherit\">𓌹</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 84, 54); color: inherit\">*</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(59, 90, 58); color: inherit\">♰</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(55, 84, 54); color: inherit\">*</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(45, 70, 45); color: inherit\">𓌺</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(33, 51, 32); color: inherit\">⛓</mark></span></p><p><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #005533; color: inherit\">⊗　𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏𝒂'𝒔 𝒓𝒐𝒍𝒆 </mark></strong>→ monster / mythological creature of any kind, a prisoner — either locked up because you were dangerous, or the humans are just being racist… again.</p><p><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #005533; color: inherit\">⊗ 　𝒘𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒂𝒓𝒆 𝒘𝒆?</mark> </strong>→ in one of the many tartarus penitentiaries underground. you'd be lucky to see the sun.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6a1c0008-8d85-4de1-bcd7-1fde3983bf31_8641987d-3b26-40fc-a167-34293c77dcd0.webp?width=1000\"> <strong>タルタロス監獄</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/6a1c0008-8d85-4de1-bcd7-1fde3983bf31_789664f8-e605-438b-8eef-a458364aecc8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"tr